{"tid":537810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭委任鄭若驊做律政司，目的就是不想在任內展開23條立法工作","createTime":"2018-01-23T04:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T15:45:16.000Z","uid":88032,"like":287,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"e59c86fd27309d10662b2b7f5427aecffb34f0f4","tid":537810,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:50:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>林鄭委任鄭若驊做律政司，目的就是不想在任內展開23條立法工作</strong><br />\n<br />\n一個老闆，比左隻鑊叫你做，你唔想做，最簡單既方法，就係將隻鑊再卸落去比隻跛腳鴨做，隻跛腳鴨都自身難保，隻鑊Kick off唔到，自己成功完成任期高升，Yeah！<br />\n<br />\n林鄭上台做特首之前同之後，曾多次提出23條立法難過普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171221/57608590\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57608590&d=0eq4qu%2FtDuichQRPO94KhRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b9004781\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57608590&h=c3919b24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171221/57608590</a><br />\n<br />\n但中央既態度，香港未立23條，不少威脅國家主權的隱患未清除，多次重提需要立23條<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/133379/%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E7%8E%8B%E5%BF%97%E6%B0%91-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%AA%E7%AB%8B23%E6%A2%9D-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%B1%E6%82%A3%E6%9C%AA%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F133379%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25BF%2597%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%25AB%258B23%25E6%25A2%259D-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259A%25B1%25E6%2582%25A3%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25B8%2585%25E9%2599%25A4&d=0eq4qu%2FtDuichQRPO94KhRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=06ca56b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/133379/%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E7%8E%8B%E5%BF%97%E6%B0%91-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%AA%E7%AB%8B23%E6%A2%9D-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%B1%E6%82%A3%E6%9C%AA%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n頂頭老闆要林鄭立23條，但林鄭23條係隻大鑊黎，袁國強識相當然君子不立危牆下，早D翻出去開Chamber搵真銀，咁林鄭就搵鄭若驊呢隻跛腳鴨黎做律政司，先讓大家就住潛建問題煲下煲下，再個社會Attention轉移翻落去所謂既律政司誠信問題，煲下煲下過一年半載，林鄭剩翻既任期都唔夠時間展開23條立法工作，咁就成功退位收工<br />\n<br />\n林鄭係一個極為老練既公務員，仲係出任第一任發展局局長，唐唐出事果時佢係第一線，佢揀人果時，點會唔清楚潛建呢D鑊氣野要避，但林鄭就偏偏揀個鄭若驊黎做律政司，可見林鄭既政治手段係幾高章<br />\n<br />\n為左香港既未來，盡量延遲23條立法，各位應該順住呢套劇情黎玩，有幾大力得幾大力咁追擊鄭若驊，盡量將鄭若驊冚入係潛建呢個泥沼入面，成件事越煲得耐，23條立法越無機會係林鄭呢個任期內成事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f133ea36581acf6c7a38cf58d55692d4784b20e5","tid":537810,"uid":114633,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"有d見地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6036745d5ee9dc5fce8cfe905ee64ca9257b8e09","tid":537810,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcc619ccd96c75dd02f445cb0263c11ce882a50","tid":537810,"uid":48083,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:55:06.000Z","msg":"但隔離post有人發夢講係777之前請過佢4次都唔制<br />\n跟住冇啦啦又肯做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00afcbe42c434a0c5cde29078fdbc626812e7d1","tid":537810,"uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T04:55:50.000Z","msg":"撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc7b42619e8afbf83d82fdb1b23f296cb859c7f","tid":537810,"uid":164730,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201